<P class="MsoNormal" style="text-align:justify;text-indent:57.6pt;">APPEAL from a judgment of the British Columbia Court of
Appeal (Donald, Mackenzie and Lowry&nbsp;JJ.A.), 2007 BCCA 592, 73 B.C.L.R.
